propertysuggester-desc: Suggere proprietates quando se adde declarationes Wikibase.
apihelp-wbsgetsuggestions-description: Modulo API pro obtener suggestiones de proprietates supplementari a adder a un entitate Wikibase. Le modulo API es concipite pro uso per le widget suggestor quando usatores modifica entitates Wikibase.
apihelp-wbsgetsuggestions-example-2: Obtener suggestiones pro entitate Q4 ab rango 10 a 15
apihelp-wbsgetsuggestions-example-3: Obtener suggestiones pro le combination de proprietates P21 e P31
apihelp-wbsgetsuggestions-example-4: Obtener suggestiones pro le qualificatores que es usate pro P21
apihelp-wbsgetsuggestions-example-5: Obtener suggestiones pro le referentias que es usate con P21
apihelp-wbsgetsuggestions-param-entity: Suggerer proprietates pro le entitate date, a base del lista existente de proprietates que le entitate ha.
apihelp-wbsgetsuggestions-param-properti: Suggerer proprietates supplementari pro le lista date de proprietates.
apihelp-wbsgetsuggestions-param-size: Specificar le numero de suggestiones a retornar.
